    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "CONTINENTAL\n000000000009909\n09090505097590091",
      "The Proud Bird\nCONTINENTAL AIRLINES\nServing the colorful South Pacific, Continental's newest\nDC-10 series 30 aircraft are the ultimate in travel con-\nvenience, offering fine food, top quality beverages and\nhigh fidelity stereo headphones. In First Class, pas.\nsengers stretch out on special Sleeper Seats for max-\nimum comfort. You'll experience a \"feeling of pride\"\nwhen you fly a Continental DC-10-30 between Los\nAngeles, Hawaii, Fiji, New Zealand and Australia.\nPLACE\nSTAMP\nHERE\nA John D. Clayton photograph\n20151166"
    ],
